;/strong>;，现在只需 129.99 美元（折扣 30 美元），&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .amazon.com/dp/B0CFPJYX7P?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;， &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cnjwkQF26Rf&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?subId1=vergedeals112224&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Famazon-kindle-paperwhite-2024-black %2F-%2FA-91563138&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目标&lt;/a>;。遗憾的是，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23409106/amazon-kindle-2022-e-reader-review-test-price-specs-features&quot;>;Kindle Colorsoft&lt;/a>;（第一个带彩色显示屏）和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/16/24271627/amazon-kindle-scribe-2024-notebook-specs&quot;>;新的 Kindle Scribe&lt;/a>; 没有得到同样的待遇。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;3ABpRj&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12453581&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div id=&quot;hXFT2y&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12453291&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Jsr4Xj&quot;>;Kindle Paperwhite 是这两款产品中最引人注目的一款充分的理由...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302590/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-2024-black-friday-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302590/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-2024-black-friday-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302590/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-2024-black-friday-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-22T09:51:33-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-22T09:51:33-05:00</updated><title>针对加密货币挖矿的气候税提议正在酝酿之中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在橙色背景下描绘白色和蓝色圆圈的艺术作品。中心的一个圆圈有比特币标志。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8wbyBQjgwN-Dg61ZDWH-VYUKXbw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73740557/STK087_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_7_bitcoin.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Nick Barclay / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MBholv&quot;>;一项对加密货币挖矿征税以筹集气候行动资金的暂定提案启动定于今天结束的联合国气候会议期间。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;hOpMfn&quot;>;对高耗能的加密货币挖矿征税，每千瓦时 0.045 美元根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://globalsolidaritylevies.org/scaling-solidarity-progress-on-global-solidarity-levies-report-released/&quot;，使用的电量（千瓦时）每年可产生 52 亿美元的收入>;由肯尼亚、巴巴多斯和法国领导的全球团结税工作组上周发布的报告&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;X1kY3e&quot;>;预计比特币网络将消耗更多电力每年&lt;a href=&quot;https://ccaf.io/cbnsi/cbeci/comparisons&quot;>;比世界上大多数国家单独做的要多&lt;/a>;。这个想法是，气候税可以通过激励矿业公司清理其运营来减少排放。它可以提供急需的资金来帮助不太富裕的人......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302303/crypto-mining-climate- Change-levy-tax-bitcoin&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302303/crypto-mining-climate-change-levy-tax-bitcoin" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/22/24302303/crypto-mining-climate-change-levy-tax-bitcoin</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry></feed>